WebDice Javadoc

Packages
org.webdice.ajax This package provides the AjaxDice class that makes the link between the project and the DWR Framework.
org.webdice.beans This package provides the DiceResult class that carries the rolled dice data.
org.webdice.constants This package provides the DiceConstant class that contains the default project messages.
org.webdice.exception This package provides the DiceException class that is the main Exception class.
org.webdice.factory This package provides the DiceFactory class that creates a dice with a give faces number.
org.webdice.model This package provides the Dice class that is the core for all the project.
